English:
... [panting] Hand me some ammo! 
... I can't. <size=200%><color=red>That was all of it.</size></color>
... Shit.
Description: Warden Intel messages like these, with the >... symbols, are transcriptions of voice recordings.

... [Halète] J'ai besoin de munitions ! 
... C'est pas possible. <size=200%><color=red>On est à court.</size></color>
... Bordel.

… [ansimando] Passami delle munizioni!

… Geht nicht. <size=200%><color=red>Das war alles, was wir hatten.</size></color>
